title: The All Muller Episode
description: A special All-Muller Episode of the Show! Too many crazy things have happened since we last recorded, so we spent the entire show doing an extended Muller award. Nominations include: The Marvel Stadium roof Ben Stokes' hair Matthew Wade abusing his equipment Withdrawn mankads And much, much more Sign up to Dan's substack for all your World Cup content over at newsletter.liebcricket.com Learn more about your ad choices. author: Dan Liebke, Cat Jones
